  • Packages that use INodeContext 
    Package Description
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.metapath.xdm
    Provides an implementation of the gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.metapath.xdm nodes using underlying bound objects.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.metapath.ast
    An implementation of an abstract syntax tree representation of a compiled Metapath expression.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.metapath.evaluate
    Support for evaluating a Metapath expression against bound objects.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.metapath.function
    Support for rendering paths to bound object nodes and Metaschema definitions resulting from evaluating a Metapath.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.metapath.item
    The Metapath type system, which overlays the Metaschema type system defined in gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.datatype.adapter.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.metapath.xdm
    A node-based extended data model used by Metapath to navigate a tree of bound objects.
